import{_ as a,W as e,X as t,a0 as r}from"./framework.e8a0537a.js";const i={},c=r('<h1 id="安装" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#安装" aria-hidden="true">#</a> 安装</h1><p>使用Hyper-v创建虚拟机安装uos系统，关于Hyper-V的基本用法可以看另一个文章</p><p><img src="https://gitee.com/AZRNG/picture-storage/raw/master/kbms/1624787324211-1379e839-6ddd-427e-ad77-d2125c9e8f97.png" alt="img" loading="lazy"></p><p>选择语言然后同意协议点击下一步进入硬盘分区，这里需要满足一定的磁盘大小才能下一步</p><p><img src="https://gitee.com/AZRNG/picture-storage/raw/master/kbms/1630137177150-534cfaeb-dfcc-4ff2-a753-2465d076ba96.png" alt="img" loading="lazy"></p><p>选择盘符然后直接下一步，就开始漫长的安装步骤</p><p><img src="https://gitee.com/AZRNG/picture-storage/raw/master/kbms/1630137286099-349e617d-0fc5-4f36-9b41-d336df020109.png" alt="img" loading="lazy"></p><p>安装完成</p><p><img src="https://gitee.com/AZRNG/picture-storage/raw/master/kbms/1630137395360-8b905c7c-e8cc-430c-a275-3313a40c76e8.png" alt="img" loading="lazy"></p><p>上面提示安装成功点击立即重启并立即拔出安装介质，可是我不是用U盘装的咋拔出介质，然后我就陷入了重启=&gt;安装=&gt;重启的死循环中，后来终于反应过来，打开Htper-V管理器，选择指定虚拟机然后点击右下角设置</p><p><img src="https://gitee.com/AZRNG/picture-storage/raw/master/kbms/1630137525439-a2ae6389-3ad5-4307-be6e-cb21c310072b.png" alt="img" loading="lazy"></p><p>将这里修改为无</p><p><img src="https://gitee.com/AZRNG/picture-storage/raw/master/kbms/1630137657831-b1ac8931-63bd-4882-8d50-d28486565e85.png" alt="img" loading="lazy"></p><p>然后点击立即重启</p><p><img src="https://gitee.com/AZRNG/picture-storage/raw/master/kbms/1630137709074-da2765d2-145a-4ca4-b841-96025c8e5a20.png" alt="img" loading="lazy"></p><p>点击回车进入系统，然后这次就可以选择时区并创建账户</p><p><img src="https://gitee.com/AZRNG/picture-storage/raw/master/kbms/1630138017581-618959b3-9966-48a8-aced-bb11301f1fe9.png" alt="img" loading="lazy"></p><p>点击下一步</p><p><img src="https://gitee.com/AZRNG/picture-storage/raw/master/kbms/1630137906180-4930f2be-b90f-4a4f-9b1f-1da3d9d528d4.png" alt="img" loading="lazy"></p><p>等待几分钟后</p><p><img src="https://gitee.com/AZRNG/picture-storage/raw/master/kbms/1630138013355-c84e5ffa-e6c7-4d17-88c8-fe6816cb7d67.png" alt="img" loading="lazy"></p><p>输入刚才设置的密码下一步，然后这里我们选择普通模式</p><p><img src="https://gitee.com/AZRNG/picture-storage/raw/master/kbms/1630138158181-2802218a-e334-451b-8e2c-29ae29f2d1f5.png" alt="img" loading="lazy"></p><p>这种终于可以进入系统了</p><h1 id="查看系统" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#查看系统" aria-hidden="true">#</a> 查看系统</h1><p>下面会贴一些常见功能的界面，因为这个没连上网，所以也不能装个应用玩</p><h2 id="系统主界面" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#系统主界面" aria-hidden="true">#</a> 系统主界面</h2><p><img src="https://gitee.com/AZRNG/picture-storage/raw/master/kbms/1630138245087-2cbf13d3-60f9-4463-8f1b-e85da85b89a1.png" alt="img" loading="lazy"></p><p><img src="https://gitee.com/AZRNG/picture-storage/raw/master/kbms/1630138822511-613b0de9-c001-446b-8b05-98d864cc2855.png" alt="img" loading="lazy"></p><h2 id="计算机" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#计算机" aria-hidden="true">#</a> 计算机</h2><p><img src="https://gitee.com/AZRNG/picture-storage/raw/master/kbms/1630138406837-b4752645-aa26-4e31-88cd-094789209b20.png" alt="img" loading="lazy"></p><h2 id="视频播放" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#视频播放" aria-hidden="true">#</a> 视频播放</h2><p><img src="https://gitee.com/AZRNG/picture-storage/raw/master/kbms/1630138517569-34972655-41b5-4673-b01a-ab3f0c96c5b5.png" alt="img" loading="lazy"></p><h2 id="浏览器" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#浏览器" aria-hidden="true">#</a> 浏览器</h2><p><img src="https://gitee.com/AZRNG/picture-storage/raw/master/kbms/1630138585493-26aa42c8-6257-4b8f-bfb5-4d976d6f7803.png" alt="img" loading="lazy"></p><h2 id="日历" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#日历" aria-hidden="true">#</a> 日历</h2><p><img src="https://gitee.com/AZRNG/picture-storage/raw/master/kbms/1630138893597-dc20c340-1a5e-4881-91cb-bc77bc7d4cf0.png" alt="img" loading="lazy"></p><h2 id="应用商店" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#应用商店" aria-hidden="true">#</a> 应用商店</h2><p>未联网状态，听说日常的软件都已经有的</p><p><img src="https://gitee.com/AZRNG/picture-storage/raw/master/kbms/1630138646191-18c8e1a0-4663-4bf1-9d07-530825beab10.png" alt="img" loading="lazy"></p><h2 id="设置" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#设置" aria-hidden="true">#</a> 设置</h2><p><img src="https://gitee.com/AZRNG/picture-storage/raw/master/kbms/1630138541802-b61d5b23-fc4e-48c9-9aef-d67b4e822f28.png" alt="img" loading="lazy"></p><p>系统信息</p><p><img src="https://gitee.com/AZRNG/picture-storage/raw/master/kbms/1630138759524-6c353988-68a1-4ee2-be6f-2841318b6add.png" alt="img" loading="lazy"></p><h2 id="关机界面" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#关机界面" aria-hidden="true">#</a> 关机界面</h2><p><img src="https://gitee.com/AZRNG/picture-storage/raw/master/kbms/1630138995731-791a9c46-55c0-492e-a99c-2aff83bfb310.png" alt="img" loading="lazy"></p><h1 id="体验总结" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#体验总结" aria-hidden="true">#</a> 体验总结</h1><p>这次我是在虚拟机里面跑的，多少有点卡顿，不过还是感觉不错的，因为日常的功能都有，这次也是满足了我的好奇心。</p>',48),p=[c];function s(g,d){return e(),t("div",null,p)}const h=a(i,[["render",s],["__file","uos.html.vue"]]);export{h as default};
